{"tha-ap41:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap41:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap41:0.3":"Dhammacakkikattheraapadana ","tha-ap41:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap41:1.2":"sihasanassa sammukha; ","tha-ap41:1.3":"Dhammacakkam me thapitam, ","tha-ap41:1.4":"sukatam vinnuvannitam. ","tha-ap41:2.1":"Caruvannova sobhami, ","tha-ap41:2.2":"sayoggabalavahano; ","tha-ap41:2.3":"Parivarenti mam niccam, ","tha-ap41:2.4":"anuyanta bahujjana. ","tha-ap41:3.1":"Satthituriyasahassehi, ","tha-ap41:3.2":"paricaremaham sada; ","tha-ap41:3.3":"Parivarena sobhami, ","tha-ap41:3.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap41:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap41:4.2":"yam cakkam thapayim aham; ","tha-ap41:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap41:4.4":"dhammacakkassidam phalam. ","tha-ap41:5.1":"Ito ekadase kappe, ","tha-ap41:5.2":"atthasimsu janadhipa; ","tha-ap41:5.3":"Sahassarajanamena, ","tha-ap41:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap41:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap41:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap41:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap41:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhammacakkiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap41:8.1":"Dhammacakkikattherassapadanam navamam. "}